component_output = jumpcheck + ",\"" + deviceconncheck + "\",\"" + devconn1 + "\",\"" + devconn2 + "\""; component_output;
devconn1="Issue - Login Failed-no output for ssh login"; devconn1;

component_output="\"" + affected_host + "\",\"" + devicehostname +"\",\"" + cmdb_tier +"\",\"" + jumpcheck + "\",\"NA\",\"NA\",\"NA\",\"Could not connect to jumpost while trying to connect to: "+ affected_host +"\""; component_output;
